        <p>Telugu Times collects news, photos, videos etc from regular and official sources for all its Politics and Cinema, Business categories and from Individuals/ office bearer of Telugu Associations/ Groups for its community category. Telugu Times donot explore for private information or exploit the information received for any way as it values Individual privacy. </p>
        <p>Similarly because of Telugu Times relationship with various Associations/ Groups , it may have access to or collect information like eMail IDs, Phone numbers etc and they are all used/ preserved securely and cannot be given to or exposed to outsiders. </p>
